==Japanese==
===Etymology===
The transliteration of Japanese [[文語]] (ぶんご, ''bungo'') "writing language".

===Alternative spellings===
*[[Bungo]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

#a Japanese written language established mainly during the [[Heian period]], circa 900–1200 CE, and continued to be commonly used until circa 1900.

